1) https://github.com/thephpleague/flysystem 

устанавливаем composer require league/flysystem

2) устанавливаем https://github.com/GrahamCampbell/Laravel-Flysystem

{
    "require": {
        "graham-campbell/flysystem": "^3.0"
    }
}

Once Laravel Flysystem is installed, you need to register the service provider. Open up config/app.php and add the following to the providers key.

    'GrahamCampbell\Flysystem\FlysystemServiceProvider'


    $ php artisan vendor:publish


    Далее в файле config/dropbox пишем настройки нашего аккаунта в dropbox

     'main' => [
            'token'  => 'kQvxk2zc3yAAAAAAAAAAGBVzy0-a8Qs3i5x0C6lwzlOnBcjgs9STYDD3SStlmFEt',   //token
            'app'    => 'mybogtestd',                                                         //название приложения
        ],



3) устанавливаем https://github.com/thephpleague/flysystem-dropbox



4) Вот еще мануал http://devartisans.com/articles/working-with-dropbox-laravel-5

